{"article_id":"FW202MupmSDtuDd1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Will Ethan Couch , the `` affluenza '' teen , get off lightly again ?","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Couch drew the ire of many","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"after a judge sentenced the then 16-year-old to 10 years of probation for a 2013 drunk driving crash","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that killed four people .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Those","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"who felt the sentence too lenient","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"felt validated","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"when Couch violated his probation","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"and fled .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"He was detained Monday in Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"if you are expecting a judge to throw the book at him ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"be warned","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"that the book might not be too heavy .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"As of now , the most severe punishment","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Couch could face","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"is 120 days in adult jail ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Tarrant County District Attorney Sharen Wilson said at a press conference Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Fugitive 'affluenza ' teen captured in Mexico","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"Fugitive 'affluenza ' teen captured in Mexico","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"01:23","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"- Ethan Couch was sentenced as a juvenile","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"and violated his probation","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"as ordered by the juvenile court system .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"- Under Texas law , Couch , now 18 , would be punished for his violation in the juvenile system .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"- The maximum sentence","depth":14},{"id":30,"text":"that a juvenile judge can dish out for a violation of his juvenile probation","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"is imprisonment in a juvenile facility","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"until Couch turns 19 ,","depth":15},{"id":33,"text":"which is April 11 , 2016 .","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"- The DA wants to transfer Couch 's sentence to adult court .","depth":14},{"id":35,"text":"But","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"since this violation happened in the juvenile system ,","depth":16},{"id":37,"text":"Couch effectively would start with a clean slate in the adult probation system .","depth":16},{"id":38,"text":"That is , the adult court judge could not punish Couch for violations","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"he committed as a juvenile .","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"- At the time","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"a judge reassesses Couch 's probation in the adult system ,","depth":16},{"id":42,"text":"he has the power","depth":16},{"id":43,"text":"to put Couch in adult jail for a maximum of 120 days .","depth":16},{"id":44,"text":"The 120 days in jail wo n't please those","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"who think","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"Couch deserves worse ,","depth":16},{"id":47,"text":"but","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"as the facts stand now ,","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"it is what the law allows .","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"If Couch ends up on adult probation","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and violates it as an adult ,","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"he could face up to 40 years in jail ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Wilson said .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Couch also could find himself behind bars for longer","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"if he is found to have committed any new crimes","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"and is charged and convicted as an adult for those crimes .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Couch and his mother ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"who were being sought by Texas authorities ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"have been detained in the Pacific resort town town of Puerto Vallarta , Mexico .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"Ethan Couch 's mother , Tonya Couch , has been charged with hindering the apprehension of a juvenile ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"if convicted ,","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"faces between two and 10 years in jail ,","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"Wilson said .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"It 's tough to explain the legal maze","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"that stands to benefit Ethan Couch in the form of a light punishment","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"for violating his probation .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"The judge","depth":17},{"id":69,"text":"who hears the case","depth":17},{"id":70,"text":"`` will throw the book at him ,","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"but the book is only a few more months","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"because he turns 19 , ''","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"said Larry Seidlin , a former state court and juvenile court judge in Florida .","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"`` So the legal issue is :","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"Can the prosecutor move this case to adult court","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"and try to get adult sanctions ,","depth":17},{"id":77,"text":"get some state prison time .","depth":17},{"id":78,"text":"It 's a close question","depth":15},{"id":79,"text":"because double jeopardy is going to take effect .","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"We 've already gone through his case .","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"We 've already done a plea bargain . ''","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"A warrant was issued in mid-December for Couch to be taken into custody","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"after his probation officer could n't reach him .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"He appears to have dropped off the radar","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"after a video emerged","depth":17},{"id":86,"text":"that allegedly showed him at a party","depth":18},{"id":87,"text":"where alcohol was being consumed ,","depth":18},{"id":88,"text":"according to authorities .","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"Couch had been ordered to stay away from drugs and alcohol for the duration of his probation .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"When Couch was captured in Mexico with dark hair and dark goatee ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Texas authorities say","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"the 18-year-old had the look of someone on the run ,","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"trying to change his appearance .","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"you go on a vacation","depth":15},{"id":96,"text":"and disappear ,","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"and do n't tell anybody ,","depth":17},{"id":98,"text":"and cut your hair","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"and dye your hair ,","depth":19},{"id":100,"text":"and hide out in a shabby apartment in a resort town . ...","depth":19},{"id":101,"text":"They fought so hard","depth":18},{"id":102,"text":"to keep him out of trouble","depth":18},{"id":103,"text":"when he killed four innocent people","depth":18},{"id":104,"text":"drinking three times the legal limit of alcohol ,","depth":18},{"id":105,"text":"there 's no doubt in my mind","depth":16},{"id":106,"text":"that","depth":17},{"id":107,"text":"when the video came out","depth":19},{"id":108,"text":"that showed him at that party","depth":20},{"id":109,"text":"and he was facing a possible revocation of probation ,","depth":20},{"id":110,"text":"they made a conscious decision","depth":19},{"id":111,"text":"to run ,","depth":19},{"id":112,"text":"and they did , ''","depth":16},{"id":113,"text":"Tarrant County Sheriff Dee Anderson told CNN 's AC360 on Tuesday .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"Before they left for Mexico ,","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"they `` even had something","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"that was almost akin to a going away party , ''","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"Anderson told reporters .","depth":13},{"id":118,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Sheriff :","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"'Affluenza ' teen , mom had 'going away party '","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Sheriff :","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"'Affluenza ' teen , mom had 'going away party '","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"01:11","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Weeks later , Couch 's cell phone use might have led authorities to the pair .","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"The U.S . Marshals Service tracked Couch down","depth":15},{"id":128,"text":"using electronic surveillance ,","depth":16},{"id":129,"text":"including tracking a cell phone","depth":17},{"id":130,"text":"believed to be linked to him ,","depth":17},{"id":131,"text":"an official","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"briefed on the investigation","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"told CNN .","depth":15},{"id":134,"text":"The Marshals Service alerted Mexican authorities ,","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"who detained Couch and his mother ,","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"the official said .","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"They tracked down the pair inside an apartment building ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"Jalisco state Attorney General Eduardo Almaguer Ramirez told reporters Tuesday .","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"Authorities ' initial search for Couch focused on the beach area ,","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"but eventually their investigation pointed them to the apartment building ,","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"which is in a more discreet location near the center of town .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"The pair had entered Mexico as tourists","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"and had exceeded their allowed length of stay ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"Ramirez said .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Couch is wanted by authorities in Tarrant County","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"for allegedly violating his probation .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"His mother , Tonya , was listed by Texas authorities as a missing person after her son 's disappearance ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"and the authorities said","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"they believed","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"she was assisting him .","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"Couch and his mother were turned over to Mexico 's immigration authorities","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"because police could n't determine","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"whether they were in the country legally ,","depth":12},{"id":155,"text":"according to a statement from the Jalisco state prosecutor 's office .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"The prosecutor 's office said","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"the pair will be deported to the United States .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"U.S. authorities expect them to return to the United States on Wednesday ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"according to an official","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"briefed on the matter .","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"As of Tuesday , mother and son remained in custody in Puerto Vallarta ,","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"said Ricardo Vera , the representative in Jalisco for Mexico 's National Institute of Immigration .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Ethan and Tonya Couch met with U.S. consular officials","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"and underwent a routine medical checkup ,","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"Vera said .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"They were also allowed to speak with family in the United States ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"The Couches told immigration officials","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"that they entered Mexico through the crossing in Tijuana .","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"They did not have the proper paperwork","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"to be visiting Puerto Vallarta ,","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"Vera said .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"`` They will be deported voluntarily , ''","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"said Vera .","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"`` Their wish is to return to the state of Texas .","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"This is what they have requested . ''","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Families of the victims","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"killed by Couch","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"were relieved","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"that the teen and his mother had been captured ,","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"attorney Todd Clement said .","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"`` I think","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"it 's particularly satisfying to families","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"that , indeed , it appears that his mother , Tonya , may have committed a crime","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"and may finally be held accountable as well , ''","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":5},{"id":188,"text":"Victims ' attorney :","depth":6},{"id":189,"text":"Ethan Couch case 'bad for society '","depth":6},{"id":190,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":6},{"id":191,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"Victims ' attorney :","depth":9},{"id":193,"text":"Ethan Couch case 'bad for society '","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"03:40","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"Mark Geragos , a CNN legal analyst and criminal defense attorney , cautioned","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"that it 's too soon to say what will happen","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"when the mother 's and son 's cases end up in court .","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"`` I just think","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"there may be another side to this story , ''","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"`` Before we jump on the bandwagon","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"and do our public lynching ,","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"we might want to hold back a little bit","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"and hear what they have to say . ''","depth":9},{"id":205,"text":"Couch 's sudden disappearance reignited controversy over his case ,","depth":5},{"id":206,"text":"which attracted widespread attention","depth":5},{"id":207,"text":"after a psychologist testified","depth":6},{"id":208,"text":"that Couch ,","depth":8},{"id":209,"text":"who was 16 at the time of the crash ,","depth":8},{"id":210,"text":"suffered from `` affluenza , ''","depth":8},{"id":211,"text":"describing him as a rich kid","depth":9},{"id":212,"text":"whose parents did n't set limits for him .","depth":9},{"id":213,"text":"His lawyers argued","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"that his parents should share some of the blame for the crash .","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"Prosecutors had requested","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"that Couch be sentenced to 20 years behind bars for the intoxication manslaughter charges .","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"The juvenile court judge 's decision","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"to put him on probation for 10 years","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"instead of sending him to prison","depth":11},{"id":220,"text":"outraged victims ' families","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"It also prompted many observers to question the term `` affluenza , ''","depth":7},{"id":222,"text":"which is n't recognized as a medical condition in any formal sense .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":445,"left":0,"right":444,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":444,"left":408,"right":443,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":408,"left":1,"right":407,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":407,"left":239,"right":406,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":231,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":230,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":225,"right":229,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":2,"right":224,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":224,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":227,"right":228,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":226,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaborat